                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptus Büyüsü: Nazar"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Minyon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Son Aşama:</span> 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz Hasarı</span> verir.</p><p>Bu Minyon savaş alanındayken Qiqi Normal Saldırı kullandıktan sonra en fazla Hasar alan karakterine 1 Can yeniler.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/213387213/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8978585508027747560.png",
                "id": "talent22485",
                "key": "Minyon - Ayazın Habercisi",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/213387213/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_5218234530430832149.png",
                "title": "Minyon - Ayazın Habercisi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Etkisi uygular ve şu Element Tepkimelerini tetikleyebilir: <br>[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Ateş</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Erime: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 2 artar.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Elektrik</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Süper İletim: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef dışındaki tüm rakip karakterlere 1 Delme Hasarı verir.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Donma: </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve hedef bu turda hamle yapamaz. (Hedef, Fiziksel Hasar ve Ateş Hasarı alınca kaldırılır, fazladan 2 Hasar alır.)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/213387213/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6613835151913981692.png",
                "id": "talent4644",
                "key": "Buz Hasarı",
